Episode 9

3
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:33,480
How is the marriage? Finally you are back.

4
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,320
Fengjiu has bullied

5
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,000
those youths that her aunts introduced

6
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,560
seriously.

7
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:42,200
Her aunts were so angry that

8
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,880
they went to tell her granny Madam Fu Mi.

9
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,920
You mean Fengjiu?

10
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,000
Yeah.

11
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:52,520
They said she had the good look in vain

12
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:53,880
without becoming

13
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,480
the queen spirit to fool with the male gods,

14
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,200
but playing with spears and swords every day.

15
00:02:58,600 --> 00:02:59,560
Caring for nothing but eating and being lazy,

16
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,160
her attractive appearance is totally wasted on her

17
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,520
with self-abandonment.

18
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:03,920
They were so angry

19
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,480
that they beat their breast and stamped their feet.

20
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:11,600
How did her granny say?

21
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,520
Naturally she stood by Fengjiu,

22
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,920
blaming her aunts

23
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,120
and saying that the youths that they introduced

24
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,480
were not good enough.

25
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,720
Now she is thinking of

26
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:24,520
finding someone for Fengjiu by herself.

27
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,520
Probably, she wants to

28
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,400
find someone from a family holding high
official positions for at least three generations

29
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:31,120
with real power and handsome look.

30
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,800
He can't be a warrior.

31
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:36,600
Only in this way can he match with Fengjiu.

32
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,720
And their baby fox in the future

33
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,960
can be cleverer and cuter.

34
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,560
She won't disgrace the red fox clan

35
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,760
and nine-tailed white fox clan.

36
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,480
Only these requirements will make
most of the youth among the gods

37
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,160
lose the chance.

38
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,920
This is just some general requirements.

39
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,480
As for the details,

40
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,280
she will list them after she returns

41
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,360
and ask my father to help Fengjiu choose her husband carefully.

42
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,000
It's a pity that they don't know

43
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,960
Fengjiu has chosen a perfect husband.

44
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,360
Not exactly so.

45
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,880
Having forgotten most of them,

46
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:15,120
she is now as lively as before.

47
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,720
If she really forgets everything,

48
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,200
you won't see such a scene.

49
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:37,640
You know how difficult it is to make the peach blossom wine.

50
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:41,080
She has learned to make it day after day without rest and sleep,

51
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,640
and made lots of wine.

52
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,960
She is forcing herself to stop thinking of him.

53
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,520
As the only grandchild in the Bai family,

54
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,360
she is loved in every possible means.

55
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,960
Why can't she have a happy marriage?

56
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,120
Jingwei, don't complain to me any more.

57
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,920
Did you hear what I said?

58
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,080
Got it, Sister Fengjiu.

59
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,720
Shall we go down the mountain by foot

60
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,400
or magic arts?

61
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,760
Someone is coming.

62
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,040
Xie Guchou.

63
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,400
Why are you here?

64
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,080
Go back first.

65
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,840
You ask me to return alone again?

66
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,800
I will make bean paste cakes tonight.

67
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,200
I can leave two for you, OK?

68
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,240
OK.

69
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:30,720
Goodbye, Sister Fengjiu.

70
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,280
Leave quickly.

71
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,000
Xie Guchou, why are you here to see me?

72
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,400
Qingqiu has good scenery.

73
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,600
Let's walk around.

74
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,480
Recently, there is something

75
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:54,800
that I think you should know.

76
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,080
How could be there

77
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,920
anything in the haven and earth

78
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,240
that can baffle you, My Lord of Nether World?

79
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,360
People in the mortal realm have natural deaths.

80
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:05,560
As for the death of spirits, it only
has something to do with three gods.

81
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,520
Lord of the Southern Dipper, Lord of the Northern Dipper

82
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:09,680
and Lord of the Nether World.

83
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,840
The Southern Dipper is in charge of living,
the Northern Dipper is in charge of death

84
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:15,520
and the Nether World is in charge of the imprisonment
and judgment of a person after his or her death

85
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,200
as well as a Yuanqi Terrace.

86
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,440
Only you can trouble others.

87
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,320
How could there be anything that can trouble you?

88
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,520
Are you still thinking

89
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:24,480
whether to tell it to me ?

90
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,200
I know.

91
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:29,480
Maybe you want to talk about the wine that I will give you.

92
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,560
Don't worry.

93
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,520
I've promised, of course I will give you.

94
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,520
Moreover,

95
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,240
it's Zhe Yan's peach blossom wine.

96
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,080
However,

97
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,600
Zhe Yan and my uncle

98
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,240
are angry with each other these days.

99
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,080
Nobody dares to get close to them.

100
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,200
Even I

101
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,160
also feel awkward.

102
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,680
It's about Emperor Dong Hua.

103
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:49,240
Maybe it's unknown among the people from heaven and earth.

104
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:53,000
Perhaps the Southern Dipper and the
Northern Dipper haven't perceived it, either.

105
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,560
Just because I am in charge of Yuanqi Terrace,

106
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,920
I just perceived it.

107
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,040
Sorting out the Yuanqi Book,

108
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,440
I found there was someone in another world

109
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,800
who didn't have a marriage.

110
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,400
I went to check,

111
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:06,240
only to find he hadn't ever appeared in the six-realm encounters.

112
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,800
You know every living thing comes to this world

113
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:10,000
through the Yuanqi Terrance.

114
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:13,160
In order to change the fate without my permission,

115
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,800
only the past-life magic can help make it.

116
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,640
In this world,

117
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:19,400
few people have such magic arts.

118
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,800
Among the gods, besides me,

119
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:24,760
only God Yun Zhuang can make it.

120
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,080
Tai Chen Palace?

121
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,200
Could it be...

122
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,320
It was said that His Majesty

123
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,160
asked to be born in the earth

124
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,720
because he wanted to experience
the eight sufferings on the mortal realm.

125
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,040
It's recorded in Si Ming's Book of Fate that

126
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,640
His Majesty will be born
on the mortal realm three hundred years later.

127
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,800
During these three hundred years,

128
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,800
he's cultivating peacefully in Tai Chen Palace.

129
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,480
While cultivating,

130
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,600
it's possible that he asks God Yun Zhuang

131
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,600
to play past-life magic on his shadow to make him

132
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,280
appear in another world and have experiences here.

133
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,040
Is it really His Majesty?

134
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,840
Since His Majesty concealed it to all the other gods,

135
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,640
it's likely that it's a secret.

136
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:04,200
I have considered for a long time to tell you this.

137
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,680
Do you know why?

138
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,080
It can't be that

139
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,840
you want to have one more pot of wine.

140
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,280
Why are you still behaving so strong-willed in front of me?

141
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,880
Many years ago, you invited me to drink wine.

142
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,080
When you were drunk, you told me His Majesty

143
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,520
ever saved you from the mouth of the tiger demon.

144
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,680
In order to repay his kindness,

145
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:28,120
you wanted to save him in Ten-evil Lotus Land,

146
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,040
only to be saved by him again.

147
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,600
In the end, you still

148
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,600
owe him the gratitude.

149
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,030
Do you want to find a chance to repay him?

150
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:38,520
I think it's the right time now.

151
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:40,360
Facing His Majesty's shadow

152
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,670
is better than facing himself.

153
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,800
I'm afraid it's a little awkward

154
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,920
to return to Tai Chen Palace to see him.

155
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,360
You're different from before,

156
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,960
saying too much today.

157
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,720
You ever told me that

158
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,080
sorrow

159
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,440
would fade as time went by.

160
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,280
It can't make sense.

161
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,320
Why?

162
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,880
Hundreds of years have passed,

163
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:14,040
I'm still as sad

164
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,560
as I was then.

165
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:23,840
That's because it's not long enough.

166
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,640
Actually,

167
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,960
His Majesty also did many things for me,

168
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,440
such as building a hexagon pavilion for me to enjoy the cool,

169
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,200
roasting sweet potato for me,

170
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,600
cooking sweet and sour fish for me

171
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,680
as well as binding up my wounds.

172
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,880
Is his kindness to you

173
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:46,240
so little?

174
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,800
What about those bad memories?

175
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:51,880
As for the bad memories...

176
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:05,720
Once I corrected the map of Lian Song's short knife.

177
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,640
Ji Heng said she corrected it.

178
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,760
I was so angry that I bit her.

179
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:15,060
You start biting people now?

180
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,520
His Majesty scolded me

181
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,360
and drove me out of the room.

182
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,440
What happened later?

183
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,560
Later,

184
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:32,120
I scratched Ji Heng and hurt her.

185
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,000
His Majesty locked me up.

186
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,200
Feeling that I was so poor,

187
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,760
Chong Lin let me out.

188
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:43,200
Unexpectedly, I met Ji Heng's pet.

189
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,680
It scratched me, hurt me

190
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,960
and threw me to the pond.

191
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,880
It was Si Ming who saved me.

192
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:56,600
Later

193
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:01,320
His Majesty would marry Ji Heng.

194
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,600
So I left the Sky Kingdom.

195
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,920
Actually,

196
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,480
Si Ming is right.

197
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,600
He said I had a great affection for His Majesty,

198
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:21,160
which was as deep as the sea.

199
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:25,120
I don't how deep the love is.

200
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:30,160
Compared to him

201
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:33,400
who is in a high rank honorably,

202
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:37,200
I'd rather that he is not so kind.

203
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,800
Then

204
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,400
only I myself

205
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,960
can feel his kindness.

206
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:47,120
Only I can love him.

207
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:50,440
I'm sure to be kind to him.

208
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,520
As for your kindness to him,

209
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,720
he didn't know it in the past

210
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:58,160
and won't know in the future.

211
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:01,120
At that time, he was indifferent to you,

212
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,760
didn't you feel sad?

213
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:13,080
Of course I was sad.

214
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,800
I love His Majesty,

215
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,960
so I changed myself into a pet.

216
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,000
His Majesty would certainly regard me

217
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,280
as a pet.

218
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,880
As for pets,

219
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,600
sometimes, they are favored,

220
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,880
but sometimes, they're not.

221
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:31,120
When he was indifferent to me,

222
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,680
I was very sad.

223
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:38,200
Maybe in my heart,

224
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,680
I didn't regard myself as a pet.

225
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:45,000
You have been humble enough in front of him,

226
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,440
giving up your precious fur,

227
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,480
noble identity,

228
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,200
your family and friends for him.

229
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,480
You have done enough

230
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,920
to repay his kindness.

231
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,280
I give up them

232
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,640
just for my selfish desire.

233
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:02,040
It's not the same with repaying his kindness.

234
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,480
You're right.

235
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,800
As for His Majesty, it's just his shadow

236
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,440
that comes to the mortal realm.

237
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,480
I think it's a good chance.

238
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,680
Since His Majesty conceals it from other gods,

239
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:14,640
I won't ask him

240
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,240
where he is.

241
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,240
Why not

242
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,720
take my shadow,

243
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,880
do the same to mine as His Majesty's

244
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,520
and make me born where he is?

245
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,320
I hope my shadow

246
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,120
can take the place of me to repay his kindness.

247
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:31,400
When he is in danger, I can save him.

248
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,880
As for anything he wants,

249
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,880
I can help him to get it.

250
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,800
You can help him get anything he wants?

251
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,920
What if he can't get what he wants in the end

252
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,800
and you can't repay his kindness?

253
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,280
Didn't you say that His Majesty would

254
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,360
go to the mortal realm by himself to experience
his misfortunes three hundred years later?

255
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,560
Then I will ask Si Ming clearly

256
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,720
where His Majesty is.

257
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,480
I think when I see him at that time,

258
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:57,160
I won't be as helpless as now.

259
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:00,760
OK.

260
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,280
Give me half of your shadow.

261
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,920
No matter you repay his kindness or not,

262
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:07,680
I will inform you at that time.

263
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,720
You Majesty, you're awake.

264
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,400
I cost most of my cultivation this time.

265
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,400
Next time before I go to the Miaoyi Chasm,

266
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:43,920
I need to go to another place to recover my cultivation.

267
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:45,960
Your Majesty, you mean

268
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:49,040
your experience in the mortal realm
should be brought forward, right?

269
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,360
But...

270
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:58,960
Through experiencing my misfortunes,

271
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:01,840
I can recover my cultivation as soon as possible.

272
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:05,160
Since you have made up your mind,

273
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,000
you must be careful with everything.

274
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,120
Chief Eunuch.

275
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:26,440
