If you shoot it,

553
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:19,640
then it means my skill is not god enough.

554
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,920
Your Highness, you are really broad-minded.

555
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:25,040
Have you harvested much?

556
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:33,560
It's still empty.

557
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:37,760
Father did change the hunting rule this year.

558
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,560
Judging by the number of preys of birds,

559
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:42,480
it's more difficult than previous years.

560
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:47,600
No wonder you just hunted a pheasant.

561
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:49,800
You changed the horse on the field,

562
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:52,320
which will certainly affect your performance.

563
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:55,080
I can't blame the horse for my poor shooting skills.

564
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,040
I

565
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:58,200
hunted three crows, two sparrows

566
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,520
and a lark.

567
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:00,880
What about this?

568
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,560
I will give you one of my preys.

569
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:05,840
You can regard it as yours.

570
00:32:06,360 --> 00:32:07,600
Neither of us tell it to others.

571
00:32:08,280 --> 00:32:09,720
Father won't know it, either.

572
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:11,200
Thank you for your kindness, brother.

573
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,320
I don't have good shooting skills,.

574
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:15,600
let alone resort to trickery

575
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,080
to cheat father.

576
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,160
You're really ambitious!

577
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:22,960
Good luck to you!

578
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:25,560
You'd better hurry up.

579
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:27,960
Six hours

580
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:30,520
will be up soon.

581
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:33,280
Catch it.

582
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:36,360
It was shot by you.

583
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:38,160
If you didn't shoot,

584
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:40,200
maybe it's I who am lying on the ground now.

585
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:41,960
You deserve to have the golden eagle.

586
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:44,080
I am Ye Qingti.

587
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,840
Thank you for saving me.

588
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:47,160
Ye Qingti?

589
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:50,240
Are you from the family of Duke Yongning?

590
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,440
My father is Duke Yongning, Ye Zhenguan.

591
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,360
What's your name, please?

592
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,040
Song Xuanren.

593
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,840
Crown Prince.

594
00:33:58,720 --> 00:33:59,560
I'm sorry to be impolite.

595
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:00,760
Forget it.

596
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:03,280
I've heard that you guard the frontier

597
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:04,360
with eminent achievements.

598
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:06,840
I regret not to have known you before.

599
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,440
It's my honor to hunt with you.

600
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:11,560
The golden eagle was hunted by you.

601
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,280
It's not mine.

602
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:15,840
Your Highness, you shot the pheasant first

603
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:18,040
and then used it to attract the golden eagle.

604
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,710
You behave carefully at each step with supreme wisdom.

605
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:20,760
I really appreciate you.

606
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:23,600
Naturally the prey belongs to you.

607
00:34:24,710 --> 00:34:25,920
I'm leaving.

608
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,360
Where is Crown Prince?

609
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:49,800
The Crown Prince hasn't been back yet.

610
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,080
Father,

611
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,840
I just saw His Highness.

612
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:58,840
Without many preys,

613
00:34:59,160 --> 00:35:00,360
I think maybe he is still looking for preys.

614
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:02,360
So the time was delayed.

615
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,680
Worthless!

616
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:11,960
Chief Eunuch!

617
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:18,920
By the way,

618
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:22,080
have you finished counting the preys of

619
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:23,880
the princes and sons of the aristocratic families?

620
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:25,400
Your Majesty,

621
00:35:25,680 --> 00:35:27,080
it's almost done.

622
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,800
Among all the princes,

623
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:32,160
the Eldest Prince hunted the most.

624
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:34,000
Among all the sons of the aristocratic families,

625
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,880
it's...

626
00:35:40,640 --> 00:35:41,080
He is back.

627
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:42,160
His Highness is back.

628
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:47,120
Your Majesty, His Highness is back.

629
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:55,760
I'm sorry I'm late. Please forgive me, father.

630
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:57,040
Where is your prey?

631
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:04,080
A golden eagle!

632
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:07,440
He deserves to be the Crown Prince.

633
00:36:13,080 --> 00:36:13,720
Good.

634
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,640
Xuanren.

635
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:18,000
Unexpectedly, you hunted a golden eagle.

636
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:20,320
It's hard to get it.

637
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:28,960
As for the hunting in the paddock,

638
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:30,840
according to the rules,

639
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:35,280
with hunting a golden eagle,

640
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:37,200
His Highness got the first place.

641
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:40,640
He is awarded a ferghana horse,

642
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:43,200
a Mubai Sword,

643
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:46,120
a plain silver armor with gold wire.

644
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:51,800
The Eldest Prince and General Ye also performed well.

645
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:56,040
They are awarded a ferghana horse each.

646
00:36:56,840 --> 00:37:02,040
As for other people, go to get your awards by yourself.

647
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,360
- Thank you, Your Majesty. - Thank you, father.

648
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,040
Your Majesty, you are not in good health.

649
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,880
It's good to return to the palace early.

650
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:14,960
One more thing.

651
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:18,920
I received a battlefield report,

652
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,280
saying the State of Chong'an

653
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:23,600
frequently disturbed our border recently.

654
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:29,720
So the first prize winner of the hunting today

655
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:33,960
should go on an expedition instead of me
to pacify the disturbance in the border

656
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:38,720
and show the national prestige of our State of Chengyu.

657
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,240
As you wish.

658
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:42,880
I'm sure to succeed in carrying out the assignment.

659
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,800
Xuanren.

660
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:49,640
I appoint you as the commander in chief of the troops,

661
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:52,000
can you pacify the disturbance?

662
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,000
Your Majesty.

663
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:55,440
Although the State of Chong'an is a big state,

664
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:58,440
our State of Chengyu is administered
by father with kindness.

665
00:37:58,760 --> 00:37:59,560
Working together as a whole country

666
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:01,520
and protected by the Lingbi Stone,

667
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:02,680
it's destined

668
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,320
to beat the enemies.

669
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:08,840
Good. You deserve to be the Crown Prince.

670
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:12,200
It's my duty to share your worries and burdens.

671
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:15,560
Ren,

672
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:17,560
it's the first time for you to go an expedition.

673
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:22,080
I have chosen a general

674
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,040
to help you.

675
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:26,880
I'm wondering who you chose.

676
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:30,640
The son of Duke Yongning, Ye Qingti.

677
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,960
Pay my visit to you, Your Majesty,

678
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:41,720
Your Highness.

679
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,760
Forget it.

680
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:49,120
Xuanren, Duke Yongning

681
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:52,920
spread their martial arts from generation to generation.
They're brave and skillful in battle.

682
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:57,280
All the generations go to fight in the battlefield
and repay the country with supreme loyalty.

683
00:38:57,880 --> 00:39:00,720
Among the younger generation,

684
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:02,520
Ye Qingti is the most outstanding one.

685
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:06,160
I have appointed him as your vice commander.

686
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,760
I'm sure to help His Highness in my full support.

687
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:11,440
Father, you really considered thoroughly.

688
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,760
I will lead the army to the battlefield tomorrow.

689
00:39:14,080 --> 00:39:14,880
Good.

690
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:28,040
Si Ming, finally you're back.

691
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,640
Si Ming.

692
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:53,080
Your Highness.

693
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:56,720
Turn up.

694
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:03,600
You read His Majesty's Book of Fate secretly!

695
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:06,920
Only you can do such a thing.

696
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:08,160
How dare you not admit after doing it?

697
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:10,560
It's not what you always do.

698
00:40:24,520 --> 00:40:26,000
I just come to play with you.

699
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:27,720
Why are you so nervous?

700
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,360
What did you see?

701
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,880
What are you saying?

702
00:40:32,720 --> 00:40:33,960
His Majesty's Book of Fate.

703
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:35,400
No.

704
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,640
Tell me the truth.

705
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:40,520
Is it true in the Book of Fate?

706
00:40:41,160 --> 00:40:43,080
It says the state where His Majesty
is experiencing his misfortunes

707
00:40:43,120 --> 00:40:44,280
is having a battlement with the neighboring state.

708
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:45,760
It's a dangerous battle that His Majesty

709
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:47,040
has to go to have an expedition by himself.

710
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:49,840
So you plan to go to the mortal realm secretly

711
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,760
to see His Majesty.

712
00:40:53,160 --> 00:40:54,640
You said if I went to the mortal realm,

713
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,320
it would affect His Majesty's experiencing his misfortunes.

714
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,760
So I won't go there.

715
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:59,360
Even if I went to the mortal realm,

716
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:01,400
I would just glance at him secretly.

717
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:02,440
Can I do that?

718
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:04,040
No way.

719
00:41:04,560 --> 00:41:05,920
I just cast a glance at him.

720
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:07,960
I won't disturb His Majesty.

721
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:09,400
Can I do that?

722
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:11,600
What if His Majesty was just in danger

723
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,560
when you glanced at him secretly?

724
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,920
Can you stand by doing nothing?

725
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:18,000
I...

726
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,200
Of course you can't.

727
00:41:19,720 --> 00:41:21,720
It's certain that you will help him.

728
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,680
But Your Highness,

729
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,840
if fairies use magic arts in the mortal realm,

730
00:41:25,080 --> 00:41:26,000
they must be backfired.

731
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,200
As for the result of the backfire,

732
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:29,720
you can't stand it.

733
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:32,600
How serious is it?

734
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:35,040
You will be backfired

735
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:37,720
by the same degree of your magic arts.

736
00:41:38,720 --> 00:41:41,040
Not only your fairy power will be destroyed badly,

737
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:43,560
but also it may harm your immortal root.

738
00:41:44,200 --> 00:41:46,160
It's difficult to recover.

739
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:52,320
So serious?

740
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:56,040
Your Highness, give up the idea.

741
00:41:58,160 --> 00:41:59,160
Since you said I couldn't go there,

742
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,520
then I won't go.

743
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:01,600
Don't worry.

744
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,280
Just be busy with your things. I'm leaving.

745
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:03,640
OK.

746
00:42:21,720 --> 00:42:23,360
Si Ming said if I went there,

747
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,880
it would affect His Majesty's experiencing his misfortunes.

748
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:29,280
However, to experience his misfortunes

749
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:32,080
means he must be in danger.

750
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:34,200
Si Ming also said

751
00:42:35,200 --> 00:42:36,360
if I used magic arts in the mortal realm,

752
00:42:36,680 --> 00:42:38,080
I would be certainly backfired.

753
00:42:38,640 --> 00:42:40,200
What can I do?

754
00:42:43,160 --> 00:42:44,040
If I want to repay his kindness,

755
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:46,360
I can't just think of myself.

756
00:42:47,600 --> 00:42:50,760
Anyway, I must go to have a look.

